                    alt="Slide 8 of 8: A tree trunk fills the left half of the frame, with the head of a gilded flicker with yellow and orange coloring poking its head out from behind with its back parallel to the ground and face staring straight up at the sky. There are small branches with small green leaves and red berries above and below the bird."
